description: In today's video, I show you how to make my baked tofu bites! This recipe is so amazing because it's just 5 ingredients, and 30 minutes to make this easy tofu recipe. And let me tell you, this tofu taste like chicken! These are the best little tofu nuggets, you can enjoy them like popcorn tofu chicken as a snack, but you can also use them everywhere, on salads, on pasta, in tacos, in burritos, on pizza, on nachos, in sandwiches. This is the most versatile recipe! I hope you enjoy my vegan chicken nuggets! Disclaimer: This video description contains affiliate links. As an Amazon Associate, I earn from qualifying purchases
name: Baked Tofu Bites - taste like chicken nuggets!
